text: Cake is a 2014 American drama movie. It is about a pleasant woman who has become unhappy with her life after a car accident that killed her child. Jennifer Aniston plays Claire. Mamie Gummer plays Bonnie. Felicity Huffman plays Annette. This movie was released in some theaters in December 2014. ==Other websites== * * * Category:2014 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:American independent movies
